    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Emre strafes at close-to-mid range with his burst rifle, swapping to the lifesteal pistol of Siphon Blaster to win extended duels and Cyber Frag to finish off anyone who tries to retreat.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>His sustain comes entirely from landing shots on enemies, so against a team that plays around cover and denies him clean sightlines, he loses his main survivability tool.</p>"
